Name set_metric - Sets any defined metric to a value
Syntax
Parameters  -name  <metric_name > Specifies the name of the metric. Data_type:
       string, required -help Outputs a brief description that  includes  type
       and  default  information for each set_metric parameter. For a detailed
       description of the command and all of its parameters, use the man  com-
       mand:  man  set_metric -value <metric_value> Specifies the value of the
       metric. Data_type: string, required
Examples
